# Member Name Abbreviation on Delivery Sheets

Pickup depot sheets are visible to everyone signing at the counter, so members can see each other's full names. The **Member name abbreviation** setting in [the delivery sheet settings](/settings#delivery_sheets) lets you control how much of the name is displayed:

- **None, full name** (default)
- **First part only** (e.g. *D. John*)
- **Last part only** (e.g. *John D.*)
- **Initials only** (e.g. *J. D.*)

This setting has no effect on home delivery depots, where the full name is always needed.

Find more information in [the handbook](/handbook/deliveries#member-name-format).
